= haml :navbar
.container#page
  .hero-unit#thanks
    .page-header
      %h1
        Thanks
        %small
          for sending a restaurant complaint to the City of Chicago!
    %p
      In mere minutes, the City will email you a <b>service request tracking number</b>...
    %img.thumbnail{ :src => '/img/tracking_num.png' }
    %p
      And a link to the City's <a href='http://servicetracker.cityofchicago.org'>Service Tracker</a> website,
      where you can track your <b>restaurant complaint</b> request.
    %img.thumbnail{ :src => '/img/tracking_page.png' }
    %p
      The Department of Public Health will review your complaint. If it checks out, they'll send inspectors to the 
      restaurant.
    %img.thumbnail{ :src => '/img/cdph.png' }
    %p
      By the way - thanks to the City's new <a href='http://www.cityofchicago.org/content/dam/city/depts/311/general/NewOpen311InformationChart.pdf'>Open311 system</a>, 
      you can now <a href='http://311api.cityofchicago.org/reports/list_services'>request many other city services online</a>. 
      Everything from graffiti removal to pothole filling. No need to call 311!
    %img.thumbnail{ :src => '/img/open311.png' }

